Perion Network Ltd.








About Perion Network Ltd.
Perion Network, formerly IncrediMail, is a consumer software company that develops programs to "make people's online experience simple, safe and enjoyable". Perion's two main consumer brands are IncrediMail and Smilebox (which it aquired). Smilebox is a photo sharing and social expression product and service that lets people create and share digital slideshows, scrapbooks and more. Smilebox helps people connect with friends and family in a fun and personal way. IncrediMail is an email application with basic/novice interface that allows for personalized communications. IncrediMail is available in many languages and used in more than dozens of countries. 
Publisher description (from Perion Network Ltd.)
Founded in 2000, Perion Network Ltd. is a digital media company that builds downloadable consumer applications that make the everyday life of its users simpler and more enjoyable. Focusing on an underserved market of second wave adopters who value their time online, Perion offers a growing portfolio of easy-to-use products. The Company’s products include: IncrediMail Premium, an award winning e-mail product sold in...  Read more
Publisher URL: www.perion.com


